INSERT INTO service_faqs (service_page_id, question, answer, faq_order) VALUES
  (850, 'What data and network wiring solutions do you recommend for large Pacific Palisades homes?', 'Pacific Palisades properties often feature multiple living spaces, home theaters, and outdoor entertainment areas that benefit from comprehensive network wiring. We design and install CAT6a cabling throughout your home to support high-speed internet, smart home systems, and audio-visual equipment. Shaffer Construction ensures your network infrastructure is future-proof, supporting both current needs and anticipated technology upgrades for your Pacific Palisades residence.', 1),
  (850, 'Can you install AV wiring during a home renovation in Pacific Palisades?', 'Absolutely. Whether your Pacific Palisades home is undergoing a full renovation or selective upgrades, Shaffer Construction expertly integrates data and AV wiring into your project timeline. We coordinate with other trades to run conduit and cables through walls, ensuring clean installations and minimizing disruption. Our team handles permits and inspections to meet Pacific Palisades building codes, completing all work to the highest professional standards.', 2),
  (850, 'How does professional network wiring enhance smart home automation in Pacific Palisades?', 'A properly installed network backbone is essential for a reliable smart home. Shaffer Construction provides the infrastructure that connects your lighting, climate control, security, and entertainment systems throughout your Pacific Palisades home. With dedicated data wiring and optimized WiFi coverage, your smart devices communicate seamlessly, giving you true control over your home from anywhere. We ensure low latency and consistent signal strength across all areas of your property.', 3),
  (850, 'Do you offer cable management and organization services in Pacific Palisades?', 'Yes, we do. Professional cable management is part of our comprehensive data and AV wiring service. We organize and label all cables, install proper conduit, and use wall plates and junction boxes to keep everything neat and accessible. This approach simplifies future maintenance, prevents signal interference, and maintains the clean aesthetic that Pacific Palisades homeowners expect. Call (323) 642-8509 for a complimentary consultation about your project.', 4),
  (850, 'What makes professional network installation better than DIY in Pacific Palisades homes?', 'Professional network installation ensures your system meets Los Angeles electrical and building codes, operates reliably, and performs optimally. Shaffer Construction uses quality materials, proper installation techniques, and comprehensive testing to deliver systems that last. We provide documentation, warranty coverage, and ongoing support. For Pacific Palisades properties, this expertise protects your investment and ensures your technology infrastructure supports your lifestyle for years to come.', 5);
